column1: So this is going out live, huh?

Even I'm starting to get a little nervous...
You still good?

Hey! Stay in the bag. If they find out we
brought a pet in here, they'll kick us out.

Awww... Well, I guess if I can't be seen...
You two do your best to blend in, too.
We're fine... All we're gonna do is watch.
Holy crap... She really is adorable!

And now, onto the "Hottest Meet-and-Greet"
segment of the show. We have a special guest
with us today.

She has taken the fashion world by storm and
conquered it! Please welcome the designer,
Alice Hiiragi!

Thank you for joining us, Alice. You sure have
been keeping busy these days, haven't you?

It's only thanks to all my fans that I've been
able to do what I do.

And what a number of fans you have! Talk
about strong support!

Am I wrong to presume that you designed
the outfit you're wearing today?
It's just so cute. Very expressive.

The theme of my current line is "Alice in
Wonderland."

I feel like fashion is a rare and beautiful thing
that can take anyone into a world built on
their dreams.

You can find a side to yourself that maybe
you didn't even know you had... Fashion
can do so much for us.

I try my hardest to focus on that whenever
I design a new piece.

Such wise words from a successful industry
veteran!

What inspiration originally spurred you
into fashion design, if you don't mind?
To be honest, I was very shy growing up.

I didn't have any friends at school...
I would get so lonely.

I wanted to change so much, but I just
couldn't figure out how to do it.

Then one day, I saw the most beautiful dress
in a shop window.

When I put it on, the whole world felt new.
It was like I was hit with this blinding ray of
light.

"I really can change!" That's what wearing it
made me think.

I strive each day to give that same feeling to
every person who tries on one of my designs.

I want to give that ray of light to others! That's
what inspired me to enter the fashion industry.

Now I can see why the young people love
you so much!
How do you handle all the dating rumors...
What's going on? I don't get it...
Is this some kinda scripted thing?
I love you, Alice! Please spend your life with me!
Hey, uhhh, what is all this!?
I didn't realize until now... I love you!
Uh, this is really out of the blue...

Stop iiit, heheh! This bit's going on a little too
long...
I mean it! I can't live without you!

Wha— What in the hell!? And what about ME,
asshole!?
Those two were engaged already, right?
Wow, what a trainwreck... I can't believe this.

Just SHUT UP already! What has HAPPENED
to you!?
Should I also make efforts to "blend in"?
Yeah, just hang tight for a bit, Sophia.

They canceled filming on the spot
and escorted everyone off the set...
